# Privacy Policy — Relocate Muse

**Last updated: May 29, 2026**

## Overview

Relocate Muse ("the App") is developed by Christina Buoninfante. This privacy policy explains how the App handles your information.

## Data Collection

Relocate Muse does not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal data. The App runs entirely on your device. No account creation is required and no information is sent to any server.

## Quiz Answers

The answers you provide during the city-matching quiz are used solely to generate your results within the App. They are never stored beyond your current session, never transmitted off your device, and never shared with any third party.

## Third-Party Links

Relocate Muse may link to third-party websites such as Zillow (zillow.com) and Google (google.com) to display real estate listings. Once you leave the App and visit these sites, their own privacy policies apply. Relocate Muse has no control over and assumes no responsibility for the content or practices of any third-party sites.

## Analytics & Tracking

The App does not use any analytics tools, crash reporting services, advertising SDKs, or tracking technologies.

## Children's Privacy

The App does not knowingly collect any information from anyone, including children under the age of 13.

## Changes to This Policy

If this privacy policy changes in the future, the updated version will be posted at this URL with a revised "Last updated" date.

